dct_description_sm: "This is a detailed map product on states of India. It include district and sub-district boundaries, locations of cities and towns, villages over 5,000 population, highways and metalled roads, rail-routes and railway stations, airports, etc. Census demographic, socio-economic and communications data are included."
Includes associated attribute definition documentation in PDF file format.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format; IBM PC CD-ROM drive; Adobe reader.
